x4freetext: The proton beam with energies between
22.5 and 45 MeV was obtained from the isochronous
cyclotron JULIC of the KFA Julich.
The experiment at 18 MeV was performed
using the proton beam of the cyclotron at the
detectors were used for detecting and measuring the
energy of the outgoing alpha particles.
The targets were self-supporting beryllium and enriched
boron foils,respectively, with typical areal densities
